snippet.title: VG Myths - Can You Beat Super Mario 3D World Without Jumping?
snippet.description:
In this episode of VG Myths we take on another jumpless challenge, this time in the Wii U classic Super Mario 3D World!

snippet.title: VG Myths - Can You Beat Super Mario Odyssey Without Jumping?
snippet.description:
Presenting the successor to Hyrule Myths: VG Myths! Inspired by the SM64 A button challenge, I made it my mission to beat Super Mario Odyssey without jumping. Time to play this game the way it wasn't meant to be played!

If you'd like to support the channel and make possible shows like VG Myths, A Complete Look, Dumb Fun Gaming, and my general game analysis series, please consider backing on Patreon~ https://www.patreon.com/Gamechamp

Each attempt of this run was recorded live. If you'd like to join the funtimes, I stream at https://www.twitch.tv/gamechamp3k

Additionally, the archives for each attempt of the No Jump challenge can be viewed in their entirety at the Let's Strem channel: https://www.youtube.com/letsstrem

snippet.title: VG Myths - Can You Beat New Super Mario Bros. 2 Without Collecting Any Coins?
snippet.description:
In today's episode of VG Myths, we decide to beat the most coin-littered Mario game without collecting a single one. It's possible a metaphor!

If you'd like to support the channel and make possible shows like VG Myths, Dumb Fun Gaming, A Complete Review, and my general game analysis series, please consider backing on Patreon~ https://patreon.com/Gamechamp
